                  </persName> was indicted<rs id="t18460817-1738-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18460817-1738-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18460817-1738-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp> for stealing 68lbs. of flour value 12<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18460817-name-1372" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18460817-name-1372" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
